{"tid":636163,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"5日4夜帶老豆老母去東京-計劃篇","createTime":"2018-04-20T15:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:15:30.000Z","uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01615168b7cf536d00d3992fac62b4b9efd4ef41","tid":636163,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"黎緊4月22-26號帶老豆老母去東京<br />\n我識少少日文(n3 pass),兩老英文日文都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚老豆轉頭會諸多不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9點機,兩點前應可到成田機場<br />\n<a href=\"http://lazyjapan.com/regions/tokyo/transport/airport/narita/access.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flazyjapan.com%2Fregions%2Ftokyo%2Ftransport%2Fairport%2Fnarita%2Faccess.html&d=uWPqRSjJFZLVC4jkpPW5sxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=dd4c660a\" target=\"_blank\">http://lazyjapan.com/regions/tokyo/transport/airport/narita/access.html</a><br />\n跟呢條link坐skyliner<br />\n希望4點左右可去到秋葉原間airbnb放低行李同食少少野<br />\n<br />\n之後就到行程問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六本木個jump展要行幾耐,我想掉低佢地去商場再自己行jump展,但個展8點close,行兩個鐘係咪行唔切<br />\n<br />\n23號30%落雨,24-25號 60%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n23號帶佢地去羊山公園睇芝櫻<br />\n附近有乜好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同通常行到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n24-25會睇天氣做人,淺草寺,表參道,築地,台場,新宿,六本木(day1冇去既話)入面選<br />\n<br />\n26號7點半機,應該都係秋葉原上野附近行下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇詳細plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我到時會開新post share的<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇巴打去完jump展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇野食推介,老母想食鰻魚飯<br />\n我會帶佢地食秋葉原間炸牛排<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/tokyo9x/posts/1656610027745336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokyo9x%2Fposts%2F1656610027745336&d=uWPqRSjJFZLVC4jkpPW5sxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d0228d26\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/tokyo9x/posts/1656610027745336</a><br />\n呢檔壽司o 唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求適合老人家玩既野同景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad640d1e720c7c056885af751ddc5814a85e07fe","tid":636163,"uid":93629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"老人家就咪去東京啦"},{"pid":"d651e8f9d5740fd2c4c897947b927c382a6a1864","tid":636163,"uid":122686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:15:30.000Z","msg":"有老人家即係遠少少的富士山/箱根/鐮倉唔使諗，揾一日過橫濱玩下囉，唔算太遠"}]}